Medco Research to buy back 500 , 000 shares . Medco Research Inc said on Thursday it authorized the repurchase of an additional 500 , 000 shares from time to time in the open market . The company said it initiated a 500 , 000 share stock repurchase plan in September , 1993 , and it has so far purchased about 450 , 000 shares . Now , Medco said it has the authority to buy an additional 500 , 000 shares for a total of up to one million shares . Medco said it had 10 , 935 , 032 outstanding shares as of August 5 , 1996 . 
